February 6 (Released) Hefei, Anhui. A deliveryman exposed the poor hygiene of three takeaway restaurants.
The first one is located near the pedestrian street, and dogs run around on the cutting board and workbench;
The second restaurant is located in Baohe District, a fried rice restaurant called "Weightless Restaurant", where the boss grabs the ingredients directly with his bare hands;
The third fried chicken takeaway restaurant is located near the South First Ring Road, and the kitchen hygiene environment is dirty and messy. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1887524520891981825/pu/img/YjPXejYo8ZLV5d_Q.jpg
